Master database of governance proposals by WE THE PEOPLE in service of Canada and Canadian citizens

---> GOVERNANCE PROPOSALS

As simple as possible. As few policies as possible

Desired outcome: Lean, effective, efficient government according to consensus protocols

Policy proposed, promoted and demanded by WE THE PEOPLE

Bring these policies to the attention of our local political representatives

Support political representatives who vow to advocate for and uphold these policies

Guardians work alongside ethical politicians serving their citizens with integrity

--
The Big 7

1. End currency inflation by adopting sound money (destroys control over media and justice system)

2. Restore the charter as supreme law in Canada, appoint Guardians to enforce the law without prejudice or privilege

3. End all media and foreign funding (until Canada is thricving again and has excess resources to help)

4. Create a Justice Task Force to independently investigate and prosecute political criminals and the media for deception

5. Deport all illegals from Canada

6. End all taxes with the exception of a 5% consumption tax on products & services and a 15% flat tax

7. End the fraudulent capaign against carbon and prioritize Canadian energy sovereignty


Extra: Restore our national flag to the red ensign

