Index: 

- V = Values
- L = Law
- M = Money
- J = Justice
- ND = National defence
- BI = Borders + immigration
- CD = Community defence
- G = Guardian network
- T = Taxes (new term: treasury or contribution)
- NP = National Programs



-------> VALUES:

V_1: Every Canadian citizen shall take the citizen pledge to formally swear that they will uphold Canadian values and laws

V_1.1: Citizens pledge:

I vow to coexist peacefully, in obedience to Gods law and the Canadian Charter of Rights and Freedoms as the supreme law of our nation

I vow to accept the responsibility of understanding Canadian laws so I may contribute to fair and just enforcement by Guardians

I vow to support the Canadian National Guard in the enforcement of laws within Canada

I vow to support Canadian residents in their quest to become contributing citizens




-------> LAW:

L_1: That by the will of God, the Canadian Charter of Rights and Freedoms shall be the supreme law in the glorious land of Canada

L_2: Enact law that stipulates that sitting politicians under criminal investigation have their duties and compensation paused until a verdict is reached. Expendient trials 

L_3: Enact law that permanently forbids fraudulent fiat currency within the land of Canada




-------> MONEY:

M_1: The fraudulent, immoral, criminal act of currency inflation is immediately stopped and Canada is restored to a sound money standard

M_2: Abolish the ability of government to control currency into perpetuity unless by citizen vote in a national, verifiable referendum

M_3: Establish a national network of compute hubs protected and controlled by Canadian Guardians that protect access to Bitcoin for Canadian Citizens (mining pool) and generate revenue for the national treasury

M_4: Creation of a citizen dividend program with quarterly payments made to all citizens from the national treasury




-------> JUSTICE:

J_1: WE THE PEOPLE appoint Guardians to protect and serve citizens

J_1.1: Police serve as community guardians, National Guard serves as national Guardians

J_1.2: Establish a national Justice TaskForce (JTF) - a specialized, elite Guardian team with a mandate to interview and investigate all politicians, media executives and journalists complicit in fraud and deception of citizens

J_2: WE THE PEOPLE demand accountability for crimes comitted by policians. Public investigations (open source transcripts) of every politician that has served over the past 15 years. Includes fraud, currency laundering and treason

J_3: WE THE PEOPLE have the right to privacy

J_4: WE THE PEOPLE have a duty to support Guardians in their work to enforce the law in service of protecting Canadian citizens


Establish a national justice bureau for the prosecution of politicians convicted of crimes




-------> NATIONAL DEFENCE

ND_1: Establish the Canadian National Guard

ND_2: Estalblish Elite Guardian team 0 (GT0) to join the national justice task force in the administration of public political investigations

ND_2.1: GTO trains a national network of Guardian teams used for special operations to defend citizens within Canadian borders

ND_3: Establish a drone program for border defence

ND_4: Establish a network of national military bases, train a strong military that works in partnership with the USA military 

ND_5: Establish a National Cyber Defence Force. Create a national cyber defence shield

ND_6: Public education initiative about bitcoin self custody and weapons training






National Justice education initiative, citizen submissions to report crimes to a Guardian admin hub

NP_1: A national financial literacy program. Open source website database, chatbot for citizens that pays sats to study and steward sound money

NP_2: A national Health initiative. Open source website database, chatbot for citiens that pays sats to. Warnings about sugar and seed oils. National network of health hubs established, citizens paid to participate. Build a healthcare framework (incl incentives)

NP_3: A national weapons training program offered to every citizen

NP_4: A national farming and soil health research initiative

NP_5: A national council for drone research and manufacturing (recon drones, defence drones, attack drones, humanoid robots)

NP_6: A national free markets research council. (research why free markets and radical deregulation is the key to a thriving nation)

NP_7: A national initiative to develop a digital, verifiable voting system for national voting and dividend registry

NP_8: A national commerce council formed with Canadian business leaders

NP_9: A national monetary council tasked with transitioning canada 

NP_10: A national law enforcement research council to update training protocols and implement arbitration systems

NP_11: A national immigration research council to evaluate impact of immigration policies on the lives of Citizens


T_?: Establish a Treasury taskforce of Guardians to protect national assets

G_1: A network of Guardians shall be formed to enforce the Canadian Charter of Rights and Freedoms











BI_1: Immigration vetting done at the community level, reviewed and enforced at national level through border Guardians

BI_2: Canadian citizen refers to any contributing adult born in Canada or children below the age of 18

T_1: All contributing citizens of Canada pay a 15% contribution rate on earnings (10% to community treasury, 5% to national treasury)

T_1.1: The rate of 15% cannot be increased and is expected to decrease over time as deflation makes everything less expensive over time

T_1.2: No additional taxes may be implemented on Canadian citizens, except by a verifiable, national referendum vote

T_2: All national treasury spending is fully transparent and publicly viewable

BI_3: Every Canadian citizen must show proof of contribution. Everyone in Canada over the age of 18 must contribute or leave

BI_4: An immigration fee of $12,000 shall be paid by vetted, incoming indivuduals seeking 5 year residency in Canada

BI_4.1: During te 5 years, no social welfare is provided, individual must contribute, must not incur any criminal offences. Deported if convincted of criminal offence. Citizenship granted after 5 years if terms are met. 

BI_

T_3: A flat 12% tax shall be paid by all foreign owned enterprises operating in Canada

T_4: Establish a citizen dividend that pays a seasonal dividend (in btc) to every Canadian citizen (out of tourism fees, immigration fees, taxes on foreign businesses, energy & resource revenue)

By the will and power of God, may the great nation of Canada rise and flourish as a strong, free nation. 

